column1: 01960: Registered vehicles, by year and contents
From 1971  general registration of tractors,  special purpose vehicles and  trailers was introduced.   Since 1971,  vehicles which previously were  used without registration  are included.

Including 1973 the figures  only comprise vehicles with license plates as of 31 December. Before 1973 the figures include vehicles with license  plates as of  31 December and vehicles which were delicensed during  the past year.
.. = Data not available. Figures have not been entered into our databases or are too unreliable to be published.
Including rescue vehicles, fire engines, refrigerator  vehicles, snow clearance vehicles, weasels, etc.
Including  motor  trolleys and  fork lifts.
